Maka Sitaram
Dynamic Programming
How can one optimize recursive problem, we can use Dynamic programming to solve repeated calls for same inputs.
The idea is to simple store the results of sub-problems so that we do not have to recompute the, when needed later.
The concept of memoization is being used here.